Package cs213.photoAlbum.guiview

This package contains all GUI related classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CreateAlbumReciever
    CreateAlbumReciever Interface is an interface to be used for all dialogs that create a new album for a user.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddPhoto
    AddPhoto Class Is used to prompt the user to add a photo.
    AddTag
    AddTag Class Is used to prompt the user to create a tag object.
    AdministrativeMode
    AdministrativeMode Class is the main window of admin mode that implements admin functions.
    CreateAlbum
    CreateAlbum Class This dialog is used to prompt the user for the name of the new album.
    CreateUser
    CreateUser Class This dialog is used to obtain user name and ID and pass it to an instance of AdministrativeMode.
    DisplayPhoto
    DisplayPhoto Class It is used to show the user a slide show of pictures inside the album.
    GuiView
    GuiView Class Handles the initial state switching of the photo album.
    InteractiveMode
    InteractiveMode Class This window is used for implementing the interactive mode functions.
    LengthRestrictedDocument
    LenghtRestrictedDocument Class This class is used to restrict the number of characters typed into a JTextField.
    Login
    Login Class This window is used to login the user.
    MovePhoto
    MovePhoto Class This dialog is used to prompt the user to select an album to move a photo to.
    OpenAlbum
    OpenAlbum Class This frame displays the thumbnails of the current album.
    PicturePanel
    PicturePanel Class This class is a panel that holds the ImageIcon of a photo.
    Recaption
    Recaption Class This dialog is used to get the user to enter a caption.
    RenameAlbum
    SearchDate Class This dialog is used to get the name of an album to be created and send this information to an InteractiveMode instance.
    Search
    Search Class It is the main window of the search functionality.
    SearchDate
    SearchDate Class Is a dialog that gets a range of dates as input to search for photos.
    SearchTags
    SearchTags Class It is a dialog that gets the list of tags to be searched for and sends them to an instance of the Search class.

Package cs213.photoAlbum.guiview Description

This package contains all GUI related classes. The main class of PhotoAlbum is GuiView.
